metadata.name: "Gratitude"
metadata.description:
I am Grateful for all of it,  
I am Grateful for my life,  
I am Grateful for my family,  
I am Grateful for the roof over my head,  
I am Grateful for my pillow, my bed,  
I am Grateful for all of it,  
The highs, the lows, the flips and the flows,  
The rights, the wrongs, the lessons of song,  
I am Grateful for all of it,  
But most of all I am Grateful,  
I am Grateful for you.
